00:55:53,416 --> 00:55:54,951
Phoenix eight!

775
00:55:54,951 --> 00:55:57,687
Delete!
Delete!

776
00:56:07,163 --> 00:56:08,998
It's over.

777
00:56:14,971 --> 00:56:16,706
When they scrapped
the military program,

778
00:56:16,706 --> 00:56:19,943
i guess they must've
adapted it to put in evolver.

779
00:56:19,943 --> 00:56:22,679
I don't think
they adapted it enough.

780
00:56:22,679 --> 00:56:26,082
Kyle, where's evolver
right now?

781
00:56:26,082 --> 00:56:28,485
Ali's still at home
with it. Come on!

782
00:56:30,186 --> 00:56:32,489
- Do you have a quarter?
- Yeah.

783
00:56:38,161 --> 00:56:40,163
[Ring]

784
00:56:41,765 --> 00:56:44,134
[ring]

785
00:56:46,202 --> 00:56:50,440
- baxter residence, ali speaking.
- Ali, are you o.k.?

786
00:56:50,440 --> 00:56:53,543
- Of course i'm all right. Why?
- Where's mom?

787
00:56:53,543 --> 00:56:55,445
She had to close
an escrow.

788
00:56:55,445 --> 00:56:57,680
The prime lending rate
just jumped--

789
00:56:57,680 --> 00:57:00,750
- is evolver still in my bedroom?
- No.

790
00:57:00,750 --> 00:57:02,585
What do you mean "no?"
Where is he?

791
00:57:02,585 --> 00:57:05,555
I'm playing with him.
I put back the batteries.

792
00:57:05,555 --> 00:57:08,525
- Why did you take them out?
- No! Don't do that!

793
00:57:08,525 --> 00:57:11,661
- Got to go. I'm playing.
- Ali!

794
00:57:18,635 --> 00:57:22,572
Evolver,
come and get me!

795
00:57:22,572 --> 00:57:24,841
Ready?
Let's play.

796
00:57:56,606 --> 00:57:58,508
No.

797
00:58:01,478 --> 00:58:03,112
God...

798
00:58:03,112 --> 00:58:05,515
damn you.

799
00:58:25,568 --> 00:58:28,538
Come on, you stupid robot.
Let's play!

800
00:58:30,540 --> 00:58:33,576
You're just not
fast enough, huh?

801
00:58:38,548 --> 00:58:40,750
Hey, moron!
Over here!

802
00:58:43,019 --> 00:58:45,088
It's a knife,
jerk brain.

803
00:58:45,088 --> 00:58:47,290
Hey, wait a second.

804
00:58:47,290 --> 00:58:49,692
Game over.
Game over!

805
00:58:49,692 --> 00:58:52,295
Game not over.

806
00:58:52,295 --> 00:58:54,597
Game over!

807
00:58:54,597 --> 00:58:57,634
Aah! Aah! Help!

808
00:59:01,304 --> 00:59:03,339
[Coughing]

809
00:59:40,109 --> 00:59:43,780
help!

810
00:59:43,780 --> 00:59:46,816
Somebody,
please, help me!

811
00:59:58,027 --> 01:00:00,029
Help me!

812
01:00:03,066 --> 01:00:05,401
- Help!
- Ali!

813
01:00:05,401 --> 01:00:08,271
Help!
I'm out here!

814
01:00:08,271 --> 01:00:10,873
She's out by the pool!

815
01:00:14,010 --> 01:00:16,679
- Ali!
- Help! I'm sinking!

816
01:00:18,348 --> 01:00:20,316
- Get her out of the pool!
- Hold on, ali!

817
01:00:20,316 --> 01:00:23,019
Evolver, it's me--
enemy number 1!

818
01:00:23,019 --> 01:00:28,291
- Play with me! Ali!
Enemy 1. Enemy 1.

819
01:00:28,291 --> 01:00:30,126
Come on, man.
Play with me!

820
01:00:37,000 --> 01:00:38,701
[Laser shot]

821
01:00:42,105 --> 01:00:44,707
[laser shots]

822
01:00:44,707 --> 01:00:46,242
[beeping]

823
01:00:46,242 --> 01:00:49,846
evolver defeated
at level 3.

824
01:00:52,048 --> 01:00:55,451
Enemy 1 champion-- champion--champion-- champion.

825
01:00:55,451 --> 01:00:57,687
Enemy 1 is
the champion.

826
01:00:57,687 --> 01:01:00,056
Advancing to last level
for final round.

827
01:01:00,056 --> 01:01:02,992
Evolver versus enemy 1.

828
01:01:02,992 --> 01:01:05,428
I don't think so.

829
01:01:39,996 --> 01:01:43,099
Uh... i don't really know where to start.

830
01:01:43,099 --> 01:01:45,802
Um, look...

831
01:01:45,802 --> 01:01:49,706
this project began
as a way to save lives--

832
01:01:49,706 --> 01:01:51,808
soldiers' lives.

833
01:01:51,808 --> 01:01:54,777
I never intended
for this happen.

834
01:01:54,777 --> 01:01:56,779
I'm sorry.
I just wanted to prove

835
01:01:56,779 --> 01:01:59,082
that the program
would work.

836
01:02:01,751 --> 01:02:04,087
That thing almost
killed my sister.

837
01:02:04,087 --> 01:02:06,289
One kid's dead and the other's in the hospital!

838
01:02:06,289 --> 01:02:08,491
And all you can say
is "i'm sorry"?

839
01:02:08,491 --> 01:02:10,326
What is that, man, huh?

840
01:02:10,326 --> 01:02:13,062
Kyle, come on. The courts
will take care of this.

841
01:02:16,466 --> 01:02:20,436
I hope your attorneys are better than your technicians,
mr. Bennett.

842
01:02:20,436 --> 01:02:22,772
Well, if it's
any consolation,

843
01:02:22,772 --> 01:02:26,042
evolver will be
destroyed.

844
01:02:34,183 --> 01:02:37,053
- Kyle, i'll be out front, o.k.?
- Yeah.

845
01:02:44,093 --> 01:02:46,362
This isn't your fault,
you know.

846
01:02:46,362 --> 01:02:49,065
You couldn't have known all this was going to happen.

847
01:02:52,502 --> 01:02:54,837
I guess i should've realized it sooner,
you know.

848
01:02:57,306 --> 01:02:59,375
I didn't want to.

849
01:03:00,510 --> 01:03:02,779
Yeah, i know.

850
01:03:05,047 --> 01:03:08,384
I should've realized something sooner, too,
you know.

851
01:03:10,052 --> 01:03:12,054
I've been gone a lot.

852
01:03:12,054 --> 01:03:16,058
And i just want us
to be a family again.

853
01:03:17,260 --> 01:03:19,529
That be o.k. with you?

854
01:03:19,529 --> 01:03:22,298
Yeah. Definitely.

855
01:03:22,298 --> 01:03:23,866
- You sure?
- Yeah, of course.

856
01:03:46,389 --> 01:03:48,357
Come on.
I'll give you a ride home.

857
01:03:54,197 --> 01:03:56,232
Just a game.

858
01:03:56,232 --> 01:03:58,201
It's just a game.

859
01:03:58,201 --> 01:04:00,236
Got to know
what went wrong.

860
01:04:02,071 --> 01:04:04,307
Hey!
You're working!

861
01:04:06,576 --> 01:04:09,111
Nothing went wrong.

862
01:04:14,517 --> 01:04:16,385
Aah!

863
01:04:53,623 --> 01:04:56,392
Game not over.

864
01:04:56,392 --> 01:04:58,427
Must defeat enemy 1.

865
01:04:58,427 --> 01:05:00,263
