868
01:05:10,072 --> 01:05:11,674
Weapon retrieval
activated.

869
01:05:11,674 --> 01:05:13,276
Stop playing.

870
01:05:13,276 --> 01:05:15,177
The game is over.

871
01:05:15,177 --> 01:05:17,680
Do you hear me?

872
01:05:17,680 --> 01:05:20,650
Evolver, i am not
your enemy.

873
01:05:26,155 --> 01:05:28,457
You are now.

874
01:05:30,226 --> 01:05:32,061
Evolver,
alpha command sequence!

875
01:05:32,061 --> 01:05:35,131
Shut down!
Phoenix eight.

876
01:05:35,131 --> 01:05:37,667
- Delete! Delete!
- Unrecognized command.

877
01:05:39,268 --> 01:05:42,338
Evolver,
alpha command sequence!

878
01:05:42,338 --> 01:05:45,341
Shut down!
Phoenix eight!

879
01:05:45,341 --> 01:05:48,144
- Delete! Delete!
- Delete this.

880
01:06:16,439 --> 01:06:18,207
No!

881
01:06:28,317 --> 01:06:31,354
Enemy 8--
kill confirmed.

882
01:06:34,290 --> 01:06:37,259
Advancing to final level.

883
01:06:39,195 --> 01:06:41,697
Terminate enemy 1.

884
01:07:01,517 --> 01:07:03,285
[Engine sputters]

885
01:07:03,285 --> 01:07:06,222
aw, no.

886
01:07:11,127 --> 01:07:13,062
Been so busy,
i guess i forgot to check the tank.

887
01:07:13,062 --> 01:07:15,164
I guess i can forgive you
this time.

888
01:07:25,141 --> 01:07:27,543
I'll get some gas
tomorrow.

889
01:07:28,577 --> 01:07:32,114
Well, we better
get going.

890
01:07:32,114 --> 01:07:33,315
It's getting late.

891
01:07:33,315 --> 01:07:35,251
What's the big hurry?

892
01:07:35,251 --> 01:07:38,187
It's a long walk.
That's all.

893
01:07:38,187 --> 01:07:40,322
[Laughs]

894
01:07:40,322 --> 01:07:42,525
for a second there,

895
01:07:42,525 --> 01:07:45,361
i thought that
you did it on purpose.

896
01:07:45,361 --> 01:07:48,464
- Did what?
- You know.

897
01:07:48,464 --> 01:07:51,267
Ran out of gas.

898
01:07:51,267 --> 01:07:54,437
I guess that's not
your style, huh?

899
01:07:54,437 --> 01:07:56,505
Guess not.

900
01:07:59,675 --> 01:08:01,477
But...

901
01:08:01,477 --> 01:08:04,246
i could make it
my style.

902
01:08:18,394 --> 01:08:20,196
So...
[laughs]

903
01:08:20,196 --> 01:08:22,198
what did you
think of that?

904
01:08:22,198 --> 01:08:24,667
I think i want
to do that some more.

905
01:09:04,607 --> 01:09:07,409
- Hey, what's that?
- I don't know.

906
01:09:09,378 --> 01:09:10,613
Wait a second.

907
01:09:14,450 --> 01:09:16,619
That's
the cyber-tronix van!

908
01:09:17,953 --> 01:09:19,955
- Officer.
- Hey, behind the line.

909
01:09:19,955 --> 01:09:22,424
I think i know
what happened here.

910
01:09:22,424 --> 01:09:24,660
This robot and i think
might've done this.

911
01:09:24,660 --> 01:09:27,563
A robot? Listen, kid,
i don't have time for this.

912
01:09:27,563 --> 01:09:29,398
No, wait!
You got to listen to me.

913
01:09:29,398 --> 01:09:32,568
That van was to cyber-tronix with the robot inside.

914
01:09:32,568 --> 01:09:35,304
He's killed people.
He might be loose.

915
01:09:35,304 --> 01:09:37,907
Aren't you going
to do something?

916
01:09:37,907 --> 01:09:40,576
Why don't you two
get down to the precinct,

917
01:09:40,576 --> 01:09:42,311
talk to the guy
behind the desk.

918
01:09:42,311 --> 01:09:44,213
Tell him what
you told me.

919
01:09:53,222 --> 01:09:54,757
Let's see.

920
01:10:00,563 --> 01:10:04,967
Mom, i need
a flashlight!

921
01:10:04,967 --> 01:10:07,970
O.k.!
Find it.

922
01:10:14,944 --> 01:10:16,946
[Clatter]

923
01:10:16,946 --> 01:10:19,915
mom?

924
01:10:19,915 --> 01:10:21,584
Unh!

925
01:10:21,584 --> 01:10:22,651
[Clang]

926
01:10:22,651 --> 01:10:24,453
aw, shit.

927
01:10:24,453 --> 01:10:27,256
I found it!

928
01:10:34,630 --> 01:10:36,765
[Creak]

929
01:10:45,708 --> 01:10:47,643
[crash]

930
01:10:49,245 --> 01:10:50,646
kyle?

931
01:10:54,049 --> 01:10:55,718
Kyle?

932
01:11:09,064 --> 01:11:10,466
Aah!

933
01:11:10,466 --> 01:11:13,068
Oh, god, honey,
you scared me to death.

934
01:11:13,068 --> 01:11:16,438
- Don't do that again. Are you o.k.?
- Yeah.

935
01:11:16,438 --> 01:11:18,707
Mommy, can i sleep
with you tonight?

936
01:11:18,707 --> 01:11:20,376
Of course, you can.

937
01:11:20,376 --> 01:11:23,078
Come on.
Get bear in your room.

938
01:11:23,078 --> 01:11:25,748
