01:11:34,456 --> 01:11:37,559
Ali!
I'm coming!

941
01:11:39,028 --> 01:11:40,462
Ali?

942
01:11:45,334 --> 01:11:46,935
Mommy.

943
01:11:46,935 --> 01:11:49,071
[Whirring]

944
01:12:04,086 --> 01:12:05,454
you hear that?

945
01:12:05,454 --> 01:12:07,022
