from upstairs.

946
01:12:07,022 --> 01:12:08,624
Mom!
Ali!

947
01:12:08,624 --> 01:12:11,093
[Mom] kyle,
don't come in! Go for help!

948
01:12:11,093 --> 01:12:13,495
Oh, my god.

949
01:12:15,331 --> 01:12:18,734
Enemy number 1,
welcome to the final game.

950
01:12:18,734 --> 01:12:20,602
Game over,
evolver.

951
01:12:20,602 --> 01:12:23,372
Negative. Primary opponent
still functional.

952
01:12:23,372 --> 01:12:24,740
Game continues.

953
01:12:24,740 --> 01:12:26,542
Enemy 1 won't play.

954
01:12:26,542 --> 01:12:28,677
Then hostages
will be eliminated.

955
01:12:28,677 --> 01:12:30,813
