960
01:12:54,370 --> 01:12:57,005
What have you done to them,
you son of a bitch?

961
01:12:57,005 --> 01:12:59,575
- Aah!
- Kyle!

962
01:13:02,044 --> 01:13:04,980
Get going!
Get going!

963
01:13:12,688 --> 01:13:14,523
Aah!

964
01:13:14,523 --> 01:13:17,059
Get the block!
The butcher block!

965
01:13:26,402 --> 01:13:28,170
Keep pushing up
against it.

966
01:13:44,086 --> 01:13:47,723
2 minutes,
19 seconds remain.

967
01:13:47,723 --> 01:13:49,591
- Ugh!
- You o.k.?

968
01:13:49,591 --> 01:13:51,960
Yeah.
Oh!

969
01:13:51,960 --> 01:13:55,230
How the hell did he
get that laser?

970
01:13:55,230 --> 01:13:56,999
Probably the same way

971
01:13:56,999 --> 01:13:59,201
he got the fuck
up those stairs.

972
01:13:59,201 --> 01:14:01,737
- Ah, shit!
- Sorry.

973
01:14:08,777 --> 01:14:10,579
The line's dead.

974
01:14:10,579 --> 01:14:12,481
What are we
going to do?

975
01:14:17,219 --> 01:14:19,555
Got to get him away
from the stairs.

976
01:14:27,963 --> 01:14:29,832
Ali, give me bear.

977
01:14:33,969 --> 01:14:36,004
[Crying]

978
01:14:36,004 --> 01:14:38,106
night vision activated.

979
01:14:45,147 --> 01:14:46,815
[Crash]

980
01:15:02,097 --> 01:15:04,066
go, kyle, now!

981
01:15:08,237 --> 01:15:09,671
Nice try.

982
01:15:19,615 --> 01:15:21,149
Now what?

983
01:15:21,149 --> 01:15:24,686
1 minute, 20 seconds
before hostage elimination.

984
01:15:24,686 --> 01:15:26,688
Don't fuck with me.

985
01:15:26,688 --> 01:15:29,758
Kyle, we cannot
beat this thing.

986
01:15:29,758 --> 01:15:32,528
