until we're all dead.

987
01:15:34,329 --> 01:15:36,665
Or till i'm dead.

988
01:15:47,109 --> 01:15:48,644
Careful!

989
01:15:49,978 --> 01:15:52,214
- Oh! Aah!
- Mom!

990
01:15:52,214 --> 01:15:53,682
Throw me some clothes!

991
01:15:56,084 --> 01:16:00,022
Aah!

992
01:16:03,992 --> 01:16:06,295
Oh!
[Crying]

993
01:17:35,384 --> 01:17:45,227
