01:17:52,167 --> 01:17:53,468
Audio sensitivity boost.

995
01:17:56,672 --> 01:17:58,840
[Breathing]

996
01:18:02,310 --> 01:18:04,746
over here!
Behind you!

997
01:18:04,746 --> 01:18:06,314
Shoot me!

998
01:18:14,756 --> 01:18:16,391
Bull's-eye?

999
01:18:19,061 --> 01:18:20,729
