01:18:45,287 --> 01:18:47,122
i am...
hello...

1010
01:18:47,122 --> 01:18:49,524
i am--am--am...

1011
01:18:49,524 --> 01:18:52,160
am... am... am.

1012
01:18:53,995 --> 01:18:56,465
