1016
01:19:12,547 --> 01:19:15,183
Get out of the way!

1017
01:19:15,183 --> 01:19:16,752
Ooh!

1018
01:19:18,019 --> 01:19:20,055
It's o.k., ali.

1019
01:19:20,055 --> 01:19:21,456
- Get 'em out.
- Watch out!

1020
01:19:28,029 --> 01:19:29,831
- Kyle.
- Mom!

1021
01:19:29,831 --> 01:19:32,367
- Mom, are you o.k.?
- Yeah.

1022
01:19:41,042 --> 01:19:44,045
- Are you o.k.?
- Yes, i'm fine.

1023
01:19:44,045 --> 01:19:46,047
Everything's all right
now, ali.

1024
01:19:46,047 --> 01:19:48,316
Did you waste
the little tin can?

1025
01:19:48,316 --> 01:19:50,285
[Laughing]

1026
01:19:50,285 --> 01:19:53,121
yeah, i got him.

1027
01:19:53,121 --> 01:19:56,024
- Oh.
- Come on.

1028
01:19:56,024 --> 01:19:59,027
Let's get out of here.

1029
01:19:59,027 --> 01:20:02,063
- Ooh, mom.
- Ooh, i know.

1030
01:20:02,063 --> 01:20:04,833
- Let me help you, mrs. Baxter.
- Thanks.

1031
01:20:10,038 --> 01:20:12,073
How the fuck
did he do that?

1032
01:20:16,578 --> 01:20:18,380
Bonus round.

1033
01:20:23,018 --> 01:20:24,619
Kyle?

1034
01:20:24,619 --> 01:20:27,222
- The door's locked!
- Kyle?

1035
01:20:30,625 --> 01:20:33,528
Oh.
Unh!

